{"tid":1647761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人已經輸左","createTime":"2019-10-12T01:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:28:40.000Z","uid":8029,"like":10,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"af99b8b781676353bb4707da3ea196580da71ea8","tid":1647761,"uid":8029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:40:37.000Z","msg":"呢4個月黎，香港人的確用左好多唔同方式去抗爭<br />\n但去到今時今日，就算有入過新屋嶺既手足指證黑警，可疑既浮屍出現，大家都係得個嬲字，獻下花，唱下歌<br />\n<br />\n知唔知香港人輸咩，就係你地太和善<br />\n係有人勇武，但面對黑警用槍指住，勇武第一反應係走而唔係一湧而上去制服黑警，你諗下如果佢有心射你，你認為你走得甩？你走開左佢冇開槍係你好彩<br />\n<br />\n4個月以黎，你有冇聽過有黑警要住院？<br />\n根本所謂既勇武派冇能力正面衝突，麻包袋又唔肯做<br />\n<br />\n香港人根本就係一群羊<br />\n羊就乖乖地俾狼食，唔好諗住反抗"},{"pid":"6c29dfd6fdee021e745a70211bdc16d7e597fddd","tid":1647761,"uid":8029,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:48:13.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽丫？<br />\n偷偷留負評又唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56ab8dde3b2e6e2b54623f5699cf474998f5bb8","tid":1647761,"uid":53498,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4i5RcEt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4i5RcEt.jpg&h=4435ec61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沉睡年幾兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0a2b55e82cf74149a0bcaf06d447e5b40717f5","tid":1647761,"uid":322304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"195593e1c567990232cceaf26927e34b470b5870","tid":1647761,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">合法公民抗爭！！！！<br />\n咁你都唔郁？？？？？<br />\n唔撚洗想贏！！！！！<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\